[{"Id": 1009910, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "As for those who are present at Mina, it is recommended to say the following takbir immediately after the accomplishment of 15 obligatory prayers beginning with the Zohr Namaz on the Eid ul Azha Day and ending up with the Fajr Namaz on the 13th of Zilhaj. As for those who are at places other than Mina, it is recommended to say the following takbir immediately after 10 obligatory namaz beginning with the Zohr Namaz on the Eid ul Azha Day and ending up with the Fajr Namaz on the 12th of Zilhaj…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Jo log Mina mein haazir hai, unhe chahiye keh is takbir ko fauran 15 waajib namazo’n ke baad padhe. Eid ul Azha ke din ki Namaz Zohr se shuru kare aur 13th Zilhaj ki Namaz Fajr tak padhe. Jo log Mina ke alaawa aur koi jagoh par hai, unhe chahiye keh is takbir ko fauran 10 waajib namazo’n ke baad padhe. Eid ul Azha ke din ki Namaz Zohr se shuru kare aur 12th Zilhaj ki Namaz Fajr tak padhe…", "UrduDescription": "جو شخص منیٰ میں ہووہ روزِ عید کی نماز ظہر سے تیرھویں ذی الحجہ کی نماز فجر تک ۱۵ نمازوں کے بعد تکبیریں پڑھے اور دیگر شہروں کے لوگ روزِ عید کی نماز ظہر سے بارھویں ذی الحجہ کی نمازِ فجر تک ۱۰ نماز وں کے بعد تکبیریں پڑھیں۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": n